Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:07.33,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:10.14,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In this kingdom where magic is everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:12.41,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,there is one boy who can't use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.95,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Asta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.86,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,With guts and hard work, \Nhe made it into the Magic Knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:21.70,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and he never gave up, \Ndespite how much he got hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:24.75,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He continues to diligently aim for the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.27,0:00:27.79,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you are a peasant,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:29.63,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,or even if you're poor...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:33.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone in this world can still shine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.93,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He's working hard to prove that,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.73,0:00:38.47,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and to become the Wizard King!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:44.13,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,After cleaning up the mess at \Nthe royal capital for the time being,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:47.27,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and the other Black Bulls \Nreturned to their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:51.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost home, you dumbasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:53.69,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:00:58.07,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,After all that's happened, it feels \Nlike we haven't been back in forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:04.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! Once we get back, I'm gonna \Nwork out in peace, at least for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.45,0:01:06.31,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,In peace, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:12.21,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,We're... almost... there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:44.56,Ep Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Return
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.55,0:02:50.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Heck yeah! We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:55.56,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Henry! Hurry up and turn \Nthis thing back into our hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.40,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Henry?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.68,0:03:00.82,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:02.62,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Are you constipated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:09.12,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I... forgot... what... the... \Nhideout... looked... like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.83,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.62,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:14.99,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell, man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:18.03,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You lived in the place the longest!\NHow could you forget?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:20.25,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,When you go in, there's the huge common room,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:21.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,and beyond that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:24.69,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.69,0:03:27.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? W-Wait! I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:30.27,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,It was my exhibit of Marie merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:34.05,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,It was a giant pantry filled with \Ningredients from around the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.62,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it was a sauna.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.81,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Did any of those actually exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, I sorta think they did exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:41.76,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:45.49,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,The rooms did keep moving around in \Nthe hideout, so it's hard to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.95,0:03:51.75,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,That's... because... you... guys... \Nkept... breaking... everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:56.48,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for fixing the rooms, but don't\N change the floor plan without telling us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:04:00.53,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,How many times did I take the lost Yami \Nto the bathroom with my spatial magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:03.63,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wish you would've told us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:06.21,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... sorry... about... that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:07.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:10.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we tell Henry all of our requests
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:13.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and make the hideout even more \Ncomfy than it was before?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:16.29,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea, Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.29,0:04:17.86,main,Charmy / Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:22.34,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Making it even easier to enjoy \Na drink than before is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.03,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We're making it comfier in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:27.12,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,This is my chance to get closer to everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, knock yourselves out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.30,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:33.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Henry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.29,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Leave... it... to... me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:40.51,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Just go ahead and jot down \Nyour requests on those forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.97,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You guys get one, too, Nero and Zora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:46.15,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... You sure like meddling, you little shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.44,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be having a hard time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.15,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone basically \Nwrote whatever they wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:05.65,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,My request is that we transfer the hideout \Nright next to the church where Marie is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.97,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother! Now we can \Nsee each other every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.78,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Marie! We'll be neighbors soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:17.27,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be in the same room as everyone\N else for 24 hours a day and 365 days a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:22.11,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so embarrassed... I just want you to \Nmake it so no one ever sees me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:25.38,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a lot of curtains to shut so \NI can make the place completely dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:28.49,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shooting for ten meals a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:29.72,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You do that anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:32.66,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you tack on an \Nall-you-can-drink option, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:34.98,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surrounded by idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:38.90,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote that I want the \Nroom next to yours, Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:43.14,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can tell what you're doing \Nbehind those walls with my magic detection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.14,0:05:44.74,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I can mess with you all I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.32,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.24,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Like you even could.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.93,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The hell did you say?! Come back here, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.99,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-A room next door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:56.94,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess if Nero ends up in a different room,\N she can't wake me up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.79,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,I was just pecking at you because \Nyour snoring was so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.51,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:04.50,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta and Nero weren't even neighbors. \NThey were in the same room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:07.74,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that was when Nero was a bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:11.72,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,She just perched on the windowsill! \NNot that this has anything to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.88,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:16.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Henry's gonna take a while yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.73,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.35,0:06:20.24,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Here, if you're bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.86,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.23,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Are we gonna kill some time looking for bugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:27.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Did you dumbasses forget \Nabout my adorable little pets
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:31.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,that ran off when our hideout got destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.49,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Go catch them before they \Ncause trouble anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.83,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:41.85,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but that'll be a cinch. They got \Nused to me after I took care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:44.04,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you underestimate those monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.58,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,This forest is their backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:50.59,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,After a couple of days,\N they probably went feral again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.91,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be dead an instant \Nif you let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:56.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait! If that's the case, \Naren't you underestimating the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.16,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,telling me to catch them with just thi—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:07:00.64,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth and get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.21,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:03.81,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,There are three magical beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.52,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If the rest of you are bored, \Nsplit up and go find them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.78,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.11,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:12.31,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting magical beasts sounds like so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:15.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you if you lay so much as a \Nfinger on any of my adorable pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.87,0:07:20.63,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that! I'm busy talking \Nwith Marie's picture here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.00,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find them together, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.30,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's a pleasure to work with you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:26.13,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:30.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle, Nero! Let's group up,\Nsince we're all newbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:32.83,main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:37.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on, where'd Zora go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.68,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain. Like I have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.43,0:07:46.53,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then... I'll punish Masked Boy \NWith Droopy Eyebrows later for bailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:49.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a big job to take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:51.78,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you dumbasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, magical beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:02.96,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:07.35,main,,0000,0000,0000,,Woof! Woof, woof, woof! Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:08.88,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's actually sort of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.88,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Meow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:14.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,L-Like we'll ever find them that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:17.59,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, he said the magical \Nbeasts went feral again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:19.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,so they'll get us if we let our guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:23.06,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure they'll remember me,\N since I took care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They'll warm up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:29.05,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Nero, you were basically \Nlike my pet when you were a bird,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:30.14,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,so you agree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.23,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:35.46,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,I was only watching over your grimoire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:38.05,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,You were actually {\i1}my{\i0} pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.11,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,They say the more you bicker,\N the better you get along...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.11,0:08:44.45,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not that I care about that at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:47.29,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I only came with him because I had to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I sense ki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.68,0:08:52.71,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not like I was worried about you two—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:54.47,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:08:59.04,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Anti-birds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.04,0:09:00.49,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:04.15,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow! Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.23,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,You must've annoyed them by being so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:05.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.98,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try looking for the \Nmagical beasts from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:10.11,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hey, wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:14.86,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I was overthinking this. \NI'm actually not sure they get along at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:17.32,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, we're alone together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:20.22,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What a creepy-ass forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:22.33,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You scared, Magna?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:26.49,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What'd you say?! Shut yer trap \Nand hurry your ass over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.67,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I told you to hurry—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.20,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that dumbass,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:36.68,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,he probably hid somewhere just so he \Ncould go "Boo!" and jump out at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:39.69,italics,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna scare me! \NAnd I'm gonna teach you a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:48.77,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! You think an ambush \Nlike that would actually work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.69,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:57.09,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,My "scare and shock" plan\N was a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.05,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:01.44,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You think you actually can, Magna?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.44,0:10:02.91,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me with all you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,No one's gonna stop us here, \Nso we can let loose all we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:11.71,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,You sure about that? I think we're \Non pretty different levels now—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.62,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:18.72,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I became incredibly strong after \Nfighting you when you were an elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:22.22,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, then me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:24.30,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The mana's calling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:26.57,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while since we've faced each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:29.67,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I might have so much fun that I go overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.05,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:36.69,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the world was that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:40.57,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I think Magna and Luck are \Nrevisiting their fiery friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.07,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:45.35,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How long are you two \Ngonna hide behind me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:48.58,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm so embarrassed! Please don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.46,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should've stayed home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:53.59,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-B-B-B-But I need a wall to hide behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.77,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you calling a wall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:58.45,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know when the \Nmagical beasts will attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.26,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,and this forest is really creepy and scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:03.13,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is scarier than \Nanything else here, Gordon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:03.97,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:07.45,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it's really embarrassing, \Nso please don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.06,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:13.53,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:16.91,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,and catch them so I can get \Nback to Marie as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.28,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:20.45,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.28,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The hell are you two doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.53,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Well, they just appeared out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:26.82,top,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You! Let go of me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.55,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,My fear's intensified even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:29.37,top,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:30.08,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,M-My heart's not ready yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:34.08,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was a fool to count on either of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:36.97,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! How the hell \Nam I supposed to catch them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.50,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,So yummy, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:51.02,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,It's fate that makes me want to eat \Nbuns while looking for magical beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:53.77,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And it's fate that I want to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:58.26,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Finral, go buy me another \None with your spatial magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:01.54,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Um... We should probably get back \Nto looking for the magical beasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.54,0:12:05.53,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, quit being such a square and \Ndrink with me, you goody-two-shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:09.74,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Have a bun. They're piping hot, \Nstraight out of the oven, and nummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.74,0:12:13.29,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I'd honestly love to, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:16.42,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,If Yami found out, I'd be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.80,0:12:19.77,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure the others \Nare already catching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:22.67,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can relax for a \Nlittle bit longer—Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.77,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where'd Finral go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:26.14,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,He must've gone to buy more booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.05,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:29.51,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Charmy. Get me a snack—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:35.10,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Did I drink too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You got big all of a sudden, Charmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:42.57,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,And you're all hairy. And look at those nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.75,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take better care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:48.91,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The pretty boy from the Golden Dawn \Nwon't give you the time of day at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:55.75,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was fun. You're not bad, Magna.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.92,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:13:00.42,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll let you off the hook for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:04.66,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Luck, you're not leaving me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:08.43,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,If you get ten times stronger, \NI'll get ten times stronger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:11.43,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,So both of us can still get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.68,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.06,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:18.31,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't really hear you because \Nthis magical beast caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:21.14,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, you're hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.88,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save you in a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:25.74,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any stamina or mana left...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.33,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:30.09,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.09,0:13:32.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I was taking care of you guys before Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.75,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even taste good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I can't find them anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:42.46,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-And Nero hasn't come back, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.18,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I feel all antsy when it's just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:49.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Magna's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:51.82,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me a magical beast got him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.79,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna! Luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:06.74,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:14.59,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. The other Black Bulls \Nwere also defeated by the magical beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:15.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:19.12,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Asta... Forget about us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.66,0:14:22.39,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's in... trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:27.51,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:31.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Tch. I'm in here, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.66,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, kid? Who said \Nyou could come back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.21,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,You might be in a hurry,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:40.85,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm facing my final boss, and if I lose \Nfocus, it's gonna go back into hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.34,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I said occupied, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:53.87,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you three aren't here \Nto take a piss together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:15:00.25,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Captain Yami will be fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:03.10,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna and Luck were almost eaten,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:06.93,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,so if all three happened to attack \Nat once, it might be bad news!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:11.09,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yami! Please be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:14.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on. Stop licking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:16.31,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Your drool reeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:22.13,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Captain Yami! What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.13,0:15:24.56,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the magical beasts were after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:27.32,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess they sorta were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:31.57,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Looks... like... they... \Nwanted... some... attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.46,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, \Nwhen I first ran into these guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.46,0:15:38.83,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,they just wanted to be coddled, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:43.33,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember exactly when, \Nbut I was heading back to the hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:50.84,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into them after their \Nparents were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.95,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Guess some nobles were having \Nsome fun hunting magical beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:02.41,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Better give it up. Your folks aren't \Never going to wake up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:07.05,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I got separated from my parents, too. \NChin up. We have to keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.10,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now. Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.17,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I never said I was going to take care of—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:16.71,flashback,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you're not giving me much of a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:24.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a touching story! \NI'm so happy I heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,The baby magical beasts are way too cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:29.42,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:34.37,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't even take six months for \Nthem to grow as big as their folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:37.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Feeding them costs a fortune. I've tried\N to abandon them so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.81,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I hadn't heard that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.68,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:47.39,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,So I had you dumbasses catch them \Nbefore they attacked a nearby village,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:50.89,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,though if they wanted to go back into the wild,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.89,0:16:54.20,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna let them loose in \Nsome mountains somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.90,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,La!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:58.55,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Mister Yami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.70,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Magna!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:02.17,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You're all safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:05.96,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Though we reek after those \Nmagical beasts licked us all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:11.17,main,Luck,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were gonna get eaten, \Nbut they just wanted some attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:14.22,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, everyone got exhausted \Nfrom that and collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:16.76,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,All of you sure are troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.10,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-If that's how they were with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:23.48,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,we were worried about how hard they were \Ngoing to beg Captain Yami for attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.71,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess that's Mister Yami for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:29.15,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he {\i1}is{\i0} their owner. \NHe's used to taking care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.27,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, there, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:34.58,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,I need to make dolls of all of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:36.40,main,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,If you lick Marie, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.16,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,They're cute, but their drool stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.15,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you want any more attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.91,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,go take a bath and brush your teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:48.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You guys must love \NCaptain Yami and the Black Bulls, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:52.65,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. You can ask me, \Nyour caretaker, for attention, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:57.68,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they still think of you as food, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.55,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, wait! That can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:04.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry. Here you go!\N I've got some food for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:08.03,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's definitely food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.19,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,That was a nice nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Zora! Where the heck did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.69,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the details, you little shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:18.21,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,The hideout isn't done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.21,0:18:19.70,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.56,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Don't... worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:25.95,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I... just... put... everything... together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.75,0:18:32.21,italics,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Recombination Magic: Black Bulls' Hideout\N ~ Hard Rock Bison Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:36.21,sign_26668_324_Black_Bulls__Hid,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(486,1)}Black Bulls' Hideout \NHard Rock Bison Style
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:42.86,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,This... was... Magna's... request.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:43.95,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,How vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:47.97,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,The hell are you talking about?! \NHow could it get any cooler than that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.25,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.69,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,I can drink all I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.54,0:18:59.74,main,Charmy,0000,0000,0000,,I keep eating and eating, and food \Nstill keeps coming around, la!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.53,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck is there a hole here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.53,0:19:09.50,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm embarrassed, so I wanted a place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:14.36,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't become neighbors \Nwith Marie, but Angel Marie,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:16.84,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,tell Big Brother what the \Nweather will be like tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.15,0:19:19.37,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will be mostly sunny,\N but partly cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:24.35,italics,Marie,0000,0000,0000,,The high for tomorrow will be \N24 degrees Celsius, with a low of 13 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:27.75,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,This talking Marie doll is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:29.72,italics,Gauche,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.72,0:19:32.85,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I guess a cutie-pie maid was too \Nmuch to ask for after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:36.47,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... clean... for... you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:37.61,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:40.11,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... about... that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:42.66,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,I-I appreciate the thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.87,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,So, Henry... How are \Neveryone's rooms split up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.37,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,About... that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:52.87,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,Here's... Gordon's... request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.25,main,Gordon,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all share a room as friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.01,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:00.10,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not neighbors with Asta, \Nbut in the same room as him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.10,0:20:02.87,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,As friends? This is way beyond friendly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:04.01,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:08.77,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me of when I used to sleep \Nwith Yuno and Nash back at the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.48,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Man, every night is gonna be so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:13.09,main,Zora,0000,0000,0000,,You can count me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.09,0:20:14.02,main,Secre,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:16.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. I'm royalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:19.53,main,Grey,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.93,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it pisses me off that \NI'm in the same room as Luck,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:26.35,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll be cool talking with Mister Yami \Ninto the wee hours of the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:28.25,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's not happening every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:29.83,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.23,0:20:36.08,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,The... captain... gets... a... different... room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.59,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:40.22,main,yami,0000,0000,0000,,The hell's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:44.59,main,Henry,0000,0000,0000,,That... was... the... \Nmagical... beasts'... request.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.41,0:20:49.75,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:51.43,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:56.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:59.44,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,Our hideout isn't some fun little theme park.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:04.06,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,As before, this filthy mansion is our hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:07.33,main,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,After all's said and done, \Nthis is the most relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:09.70,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like we're finally home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.50,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm not disappointed in the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:19.71,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came here after \Njoining the Black Bulls...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:25.22,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,They all accepted me immediately, \Neven though I didn't have any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:28.76,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since then, every day's been action-packed,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.51,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,and we had plenty of close calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:34.48,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,but I was able to get through \Nthem thanks to everyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:39.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy that I got to join the \NBlack Bulls and get to know all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:43.23,main,Magna,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where'd that come from? \NYou're making me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.42,italics,Vanessa,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:49.41,italics,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you never gave up, \NAsta, that we were able to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:53.66,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You're always reckless, but I'll admit \Nthat you're as stubborn as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:56.81,main,Finral,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry up and prove Asta's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:57.82,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:22:01.92,main,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we're gonna have to continue \Nour research on the devils.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:05.07,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.79,0:23:43.90,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We're back at our hideout, \Nso I'm gonna work even harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:46.77,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are you going, Captain Yami?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.77,0:23:50.95,main,Some,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on {\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 126: \N"The Blue Rose's Confession."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.78,0:23:54.25,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 126\N\N{\fs18}The Blue Rose's Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:53.91,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So what exactly is Captain \NCharlotte going to confess?
